        "Data": [
          "<h2>What to Do</h2>\n  <p>Use an intermediate disclaimer page that provides the user with a clear warning that they are leaving your site. Implement a long timeout before the redirect occurs, or force the user to click on the link. Be careful to avoid XSS problems (CWE-79) when generating\n the disclaimer page.</p>\n  <h2>Additional Resources</h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li>For more information about \"CWE-79: Improper Neutralization of Input During Web Page Generation ('Cross-site Scripting')\", please see\n<a href=\"http://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/79.html\">http://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/79.html</a></li>\n  </ul>"
        ]
